    "body": "@felixrieseberg it looks like LSMultipleInstancesProhibited doesn't do exactly what we want, though.\n\nFrom https://developer.apple.com/library/ios/documentation/General/Reference/InfoPlistKeyReference/Articles/LaunchServicesKeys.html#//apple_ref/doc/uid/20001431-113300\n\n> If true, the app runs in only one user session at a time.\n\n`app.makeSingleInstance` doesn't prevent multiple instances across different users.\n"
